    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "SAC Johnson of the Milwaukee Office called to advise he had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "just received a telephone call from Colonel [REDACTED] Reserve",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Officer with the Civilian Air Patrol, Black River Falls, Wisconsin.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Colonel [REDACTED] reported that at 3:30 p.m., July 10, one [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "[REDACTED] at Black River Falls, Wisconsin, had found a large",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "17\" disc which appeared to have been possibly made out of cardboard",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "painted with silver airplane dope. In the center was a tube and a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "small motor with a propellor attached to the side. Colonel [REDACTED] b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "expressed the opinion that this disc would not be able to fly by",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "itself. He advised it would be taken to the Air Corps Headquarters.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Colonel [REDACTED] advised, however, that [REDACTED] did not want to release",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "the disc without FBI approval.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "I instructed Mr. Johnson to advise the Air Corps officer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "to get in touch with Colonel [REDACTED] and tell him he saw no reason for b7c",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "the Bureau to attempt to secure the release of the material since it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "was not in our custody and we had no control. He stated the press was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "also calling concerning this matter. I instructed him to make no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "comment to the press.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
